    <item>
      <title>Evercore 称纳斯达克 100 指数的历史性牛市还有很长的路要走</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/nasdaq-100-s-historic-bull-run-has-further-to-go-evercore-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2023 年初以来，纳斯达克 100 指数已上涨近一倍，市值增加了 14 万亿美元。Evercore ISI 的 Rich Ross 已做好继续上涨的准备，他无视人们对熟悉的对手——债券收益率上升的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/nasdaq-100-s-historic-bull-run-has-further-to-go-evercore-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 11:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行的美元销售可能再次为莫迪政府带来丰厚股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/rbi-s-dollar-sales-may-net-modi-government-bumper-dividend-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度货币贬值或许仍对联邦政府有利。分析师预计印度储备银行将再获得一年的意外红利，这要归功于其为支撑卢比而抛售大量美元所获得的利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/rbi-s-dollar-sales-may-net-modi-government-bumper-dividend-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 11:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
